":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T18:30:23.000Z","msg":"除咗轉貼屈文妓之外，究竟跑過咩新聞？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5370427a34535744a5ef2c6e0ae804568cb4d5","tid":778151,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T18:32:06.000Z","msg":"政府新聞處強硬一律拒網媒採訪 梁振英菲制裁記者會不得入<br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 早前新聞處打壓網絡媒體採訪政府官方活動甚至施政報告記者會，事至今未獲解決。本通訊社派遣記者前往採訪特首今日下午舉行有關菲律賓制裁的記者會，惟該名記者在登記處時被拒絕派發臨時准許證，故不能進入記者會進行採訪。 <br />\n<br />\n記者致電政府新聞處總新聞主任，要求取得合理回覆時，總新聞主任回應指，只要「單一依靠網絡渠道」發放新聞資訊的媒體，將一律不能進入政府新聞處負責的記者招待會，亦不會獲批任何出入政府大樓的記者採訪證，再度對網絡媒體發展趨勢視而不見。 <br />\n<br />\n早前有消息指梁振英出手，要求中資機構抽走多份報章廣告。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%99%95%E5%BC%B7%E7%A1%AC-%E5%BE%8B%E6%8B%92%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%B2%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%85%A5-101739400.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A1%25AC-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2585%25A5-101739400.html&d=7GYNeQdfKZmjoufRQVFgpv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9087a69e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%99%95%E5%BC%B7%E7%A1%AC-%E5%BE%8B%E6%8B%92%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%B2%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%85%A5-101739400.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hk